{"tid":2246145,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–油脂在細胞裡的功用","createTime":"2020-10-16T20:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T12:18:34.000Z","uid":38861,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"27d6edd0219242f8ffaf142ac6365e6d3a9f0733","tid":2246145,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:45:59.000Z","msg":"大部份的人體細胞均會藏有油脂。當細胞需要能源的時候，油脂可以在粒線體裡頭分解成為能源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyGFDWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyGFDWn.jpg&h=71d1bd16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有科學家發現(Ref1)，當有細菌入侵細胞的時候，細胞的油脂數量會增加，但相應的體積亦會有所縮小。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G59Pxgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG59Pxgp.jpg&h=eb6edef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）油脂除了能量儲存功用外，亦提供了各種蛋白質聚集的地方。<br />\n譬如說，PLN5就是一種引領油脂抵達粒線體的蛋白質。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYStNPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYStNPP.jpg&h=77396973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科學家在文中指出，當有細菌入侵細胞的時候，油脂上的PLN5蛋白質就會減少，取而代之會有各種與免疫系統有關的蛋白質黏附在油脂上，並傾向與細菌接觸。<br />\n<br />\n箇中油脂上其中一種名為Cathelicidin的蛋白質便有著破壞部份細菌的外壁功效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）隨著油脂用作對付細菌的關係，油脂再也無瑕抵達粒線體作分解能源之用。因此在對抗入侵者期間，細胞亦會因而傾向轉用葡萄糖作為能量來源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXZ0DWx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXZ0DWx.png&h=913413ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之於如何善用這種知識來研發對抗感染的療法，那將會是科學家們日後的命題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=d084898d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=9480c8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6514/eaay8085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F370%2F6514%2Feaay8085&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=2559752c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/370/6514/eaay8085</a>"},{"pid":"c27829ad08786ce2b854c5c32a416d4e84e9be57","tid":2246145,"uid":87043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:48:47.000Z","msg":"有用！"},{"pid":"d452e570c255056a25dcad98e0be6604ea9f23b5","tid":2246145,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c27829ad08786ce2b854c5c32a416d4e84e9be57","tid":2246145,"uid":87043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:48:47.000Z","msg":"有用！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx"},{"pid":"d7d9c77356436e7a826e817fd25df527d4570de3","tid":2246145,"uid":319935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10